123 173 7B  01111011   {      &#123;                        Opening brace
124 174 7C  01111100   |      &#124;                         Vertical bar
125 175 7D  01111101   }      &#125;                        Closing brace
126 176 7E  01111110   ~      &#126;                   Equivalency sign - tilde
